Creating a EKS cluster using YAML file,
---------------------------------------------
NOTE THAT eksctl will create a VPC and two subnets AUTOMATICALLY, However we can mention existing VPC for that please refer the eksctl documatation.
	
	#Creating a EKS cluster using YAML file
	eksctl create cluster -f eks-raju-cluster.yml

	#To list all node that has been created with cluster creation 
	kubectl get nodes 	
